						               													<description>Whether you&amp;rsquo;re newly in love or already married: turn your everyday life into an experience and have a fabulous time full of fun and closeness. Because this game is all about you!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Flitterkiste is a legacy game for two people who love each other. It offers a completely new gaming experience &amp;ndash; because the challenges are played for and with each other in everyday life. As a gift, it suits any occasion and can be combined with other presents.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;How to play and win:&amp;#10;On your turn each of you draws a secret card with a task from the shared deck. You can solve it within a few days. After this period, you draw the next card. Completed tasks reward you with hearts &amp;ndash; the currency of the game. You collect them and can use them to unlock added content and gifts. It is your choice. There are ten locked chapters within the chronicle. When you open and complete the last chapter both of you win the game.&amp;#10;In between you will receive shared cards. They are not secret, and you can solve the challenges together at any time. They will help you to change the rules of the game and give you bonus hearts.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The perpetual calendar always gives you an overview of what is next in the game. He functions as a game board, because this is where you can see your progress and record your goals.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;During play you will write, paste over or use up cards and other components. This is how the Flitterkiste develops further and adapts to the interests of the couple.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Components:&amp;#10;133 Unique cards&amp;#10;76 Pages game book&amp;#10;1 Perpetual calendar&amp;#10;31 Sticker&amp;#10;2 Game markers&amp;#10;&amp;amp; lots of love&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
